Detailed Description

template<typename VALUE, typename KEYTYPE = uint64>
template<typename RealIterator, typename ReturnTypeRef, typename ReturnTypePtr>
class CRangeMap< VALUE, KEYTYPE >::iterator_base< RealIterator, ReturnTypeRef, ReturnTypePtr >

This class provides a wrapper around the raw iterators used by CRangeMap.

It will act as a normal iterator and also give access the the range values. When used as a per normal, it will return the value specified by the user for that range.

Special member-functions are keyStart() and keyEnd().
